title: John Denver Discography Part 6
description:
This one is boring - compilations of stuff already done. But, I&#039;m trying to do it all. It gets more interesting in Part 7.

PART 6 - Ok, he&#039;s dead, but where can we get more of his voice?

So, this is probably a boring part - it&#039;s mostly stuff he did already.
But these are &#039;official&#039; compilations.... so....

Complilation albums
1996 The Rocky Mountain Collection - 192 mp3
1997 Celebration of Life - best from Bittorrent
aka Love Again aka The Unplugged Collection
1997 Country Roads Collection - 192 mp3
1998 The Best of John Denver - best from Bittorrent
